												<h3>Why your business needs <em>HR policies & Job Descriptions</em></h3>
												<p class="bottom">
													<strong class="color2">Clear & concise HR policies & job descriptions are vital 
													for your bottom line.</strong>
													 Failing to implement policies & job descriptions leaves your company 
													 open to legal challenges, grievances & lawsuits, especially if you 
													 inconsistently apply your HR policies and pay system. Grievances and lawsuits 
													 lead to:
													 <br><br>
													 - Increased costs that affect your profits<br>
													 - Increased turnover<br>
													 - Negative morale
													 <br><br>
													 Your company will avoid these problems if you implement hr policies, procedures 
													 and job descriptions.  Downloading our free samples today will get you started.
												 </p>
												
												 <p class="bottom">
													<strong class="color2">Human resources policies and job descriptions improve 
													employee retention & morale.</strong>
													Your company needs human resources policies and procedures and job 
													descriptions so that employees are treated equally across a variety of 
													employment issues. In addition, human resources polices help if legal situations 
													arise. Our products and services are ideally suited for:
													<br><br>
													 - Small Business Owners<br>
													 - Managers<br>
													 - HR Professionals<br>
													 - HR Consultants<br>
													 - Lawyers
													 <br><br>
													 Small businesses often scramble for resources when compiling staffing 
													 information, contracts, developing HR policies and procedures and writing job 
													 descriptions. In addition, many large companies have dated policies, procedures 
													 and job descriptions that no longer reflect the reality of today's business 
													 world. Companies looking for fresh ideas and a fresh start to can find what they 
													 are looking for with our sample hr policies and sample job descriptions.</p>
												 <p class="bottom">
												 	<strong class="color2"></strong>
